Hellplague:

"No,just walk.  You don't want to make them nervous or
edgy.  It should not be that long of a walk,"
Hellplague said quietly, crossing her arms over her
chest.

> "I can't fly, but I do have jets that alow me to
> jump up in the air
> and hover for a few seconds, so if you would like, I
> can go a bit
> faster than this." said Celeron.


"HA!  Is that all you got?  You boasted such power, such skill!  Where is your power and skill now?  You disappoint me, ha ha ha haa!"
